Package org.agreement_technologies.common.map_grounding

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Action
    Planning action (grounded operator).
    GroundedCond
    Grounded condition: (= variable value) or (<> variable value).
    GroundedEff
    Grounded effect: (assign variable value).
    GroundedNumericEff
    Grounded numeric effect: only to increase the value of a numeric variable is supported.
    GroundedNumericExpression
    Grounded numeric expression to define numeric action effects.
    GroundedRule
    Grounded belief rule
    GroundedTask
    Grounded planning task.
    GroundedVar
    Grounded variable.
    Grounding
    Planning task grounding.
    ReachedValue
    Reached values in the grounding process.
